    public interface UiWidgetTreeTable<NODE>
extends UiWidgetAbstractDataTable<NODE>, UiWidgetAbstractTree<NODE>, UiWidgetNative
    This is the interface for a regular widget that is both a list table as well as a UiWidgetAbstractTree.

    1.0.0
